<h2>Enhanced Code</h2>
<pre>These enhancements significantly improved the system’s reliability, maintainability, and usability. Logging enables better monitoring and debugging, validation ensures data integrity and security, and filtered queries improve performance while supporting dynamic user interaction within the dashboard.
A key design trade-off in this enhancement process was balancing performance optimization with code readability and maintainability. While more complex queries and tightly optimized logic could improve speed, I prioritized modular design and clear structure to ensure the system remains scalable and easier to maintain over time.
Additionally, these improvements reflect a security-focused mindset by validating user inputs and reducing the risk of invalid or harmful data entering the system.

