<h2>Reflection</h2>
<p>Enhancing this artifact strengthened my understanding of how to design scalable and maintainable software systems. I learned the importance of separating concerns by modularizing code and centralizing database operations. One of the main challenges I encountered was debugging callback functions in Dash, which required a deeper understanding of event-driven programming and how user inputs trigger updates across the application.
